Subject: Re: [T2] rusty wheels

>1. Wire wheel as much rust as possible off.
>
>         2. Wash metal with lacquer thinner.

I'd only add 2 steps more. Rough sand, and then fine sand them with water + 
a bit of regular dish washing soap. Wire brush and clean all you want but 
right be fore you prime, do the wet sanding thing. Do all my engine tin 
this way with excellent results.


